The paper proposes a new approach to enhance amortized inference in VAEs using Information Theoretic techniques. This involves maximizing mutual information to learn meaningful representations. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
